an estimated average reporting burden of 30 minutes per response. The change in the composition of the Board would
reduce the number of respondents completing this form from 44 to 28; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(8) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
