7
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

</FOOTNAME>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
 Preference stock, also known as prior-preferred stock, is preferred stock that has a higher claim than other issues
of preferred stock on dividends and assets in liquidation. 
