<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Market-to-Book Ratio (``MBR''), and Comparable Earnings (``CE'').
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=5 f=1 -->
